Class Edge<I,N,D>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cpp.cs.cs241.prog_assgmnt_4.Edge<I,N,D>
  • Type Parameters:
    I -
    N -
    D - 

    public class Edge<I,N,D>
extends java.lang.Object
    The following class represents a line between two nodes, or vertices. To represent an edge, it keeps track of two nodes, one being the top and one being the bottom. Additionally, it maintains the weight of the line as well as the street name.
    Author:
    Michael
